low noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;沃尔玛&lt;/a>;) 也在以 88.99 美元的价格出售四件装（折扣 11 美元）。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class= &quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;TVwzTP&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title &quot;:&quot;寻找物品的最佳蓝牙追踪器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23769840/best-bluetooth-trackers&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 的 2023 年回顾-学校礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23800225/back-to-school-student-gifts-college-high-school-dorm-ideas-2023&quot;},{&quot;title &quot;:&quot;我们可能要等待 AirTags 的下一个版本&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/2/23817520/apple-airtags-2-mass-Production&quot; }]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;rnJAK4&quot;>;我们&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23769840/best-bluetooth-trackers&quot;>;对于 iPhone 用户，强烈推荐&lt;/a>; AirTags，而不是其他蓝牙追踪器。这是因为 AirTags 配备了 Apple 的超宽带 (UWB) 芯片，并利用了 Apple 庞大的“查找我的网络”系统，可实现异常精确的跟踪。另外，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/6/23751614/apple-airtag-find-my-sharing-ios-17-feature&quot;>;一旦 iOS 17 今年秋季正式发布&lt; /a>;，你会...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/4/23820184/apple-airtag-bluetooth-location-tracker -deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/4/23820184/apple-airtag-bluetooth-location-tracker-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/4/23820184/apple-airtag-bluetooth-location-tracker-deal-sale</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry></feed>